The various agencies and institutions involved in the administration of the 2019 general elections have continued to assure Nigerians of the readiness for the polls from the direct electoral supervision to security responsibilities.     
The Katsina State Police Command have assured that the personnel are fully prepared to provide adequate security during and after the elections in the state.
The State Police Commissioner, Sanusi Buba, at a media briefing at the Command, reassured electorate of effective preparation of the Police to protect their lives and guarantee their safety during the electoral process.
